-last-war-experts-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2461%20billion%20aid%20package%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20voted%20through%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWeapons%2C%20ammunition%2C%20and%20military%20hardware%20from%20US%20stockpiles%20are%20expected%20to%20make%20up%20at%20least%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.csis.org%2Fanalysis%2Fwhat-ukraine-aid-package-and-what-does-it-mean-future-war%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2425%20billion%20of%20the%20funding.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Abrams%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fabrams-tank-built-to-kill-tanks-destroy-soviet-russian-armor-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edefeated%20Soviet%20armor%20before%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20several%20deployed%20in%20Ukraine%20have%20suffered%20setbacks.%20At%20least%20five%20of%20the%20tanks%20were%20lost%20in%20combat%2C%20and%20another%20three%20were%20damaged%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F04%2F20%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Ftanks-ukraine-drones-abrams.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20late%20April%2C%20the%20Russian%20military%20displayed%20an%20abandoned%20Abrams%20M1A1%20at%20an%20exhibition%20called%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-displaying-war-trophies-like-abrams-and-leopard-tanks-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BTrophies%20of%20the%20Russian%20Army%2C%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewhich%20showcased%20NATO%20equipment%20seized%20during%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukrainian-tank-crew-says-abrams-easy-drive-scooter-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715155477000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663b2c7ab4abc992e8c6c7ee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsid