20fury%20-%20Ghaziabad's%20latest%20crime%20story%20looks%20like%20a%20page%20taken%20out%20of%20a%20David%20Baldacci%20novel.%20The%20victim%2C%20an%2018-year-old%20woman%20named%20Jyoti%2C%20had%20travelled%20from%20her%20in-laws'%20home%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Babrala%20town%20to%20care%20for%20her%20ailing%20mother%2C%20Champa%20Devi%20who%20is%20a%20cancer%20patient%2C%20in%20Ghaziabad's%20Indirapuram%20area.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELalitesh%2C%20Jyoti's%20husband%20and%20an%20e-rickshaw%20driver%20accompanied%20her%20to%20Champa%20Devi's%20home.%20On%20Tuesday%2C%20a%20man%20identified%20as%20Bobby%20unleashed%20a%20frenzied%20knife%20attack%20on%20Champa%20Devi.%20In%20an%20attempt%20to%20shield%20her%2C%20Jyoti%20and%20Lalitesh%20intervened%2C%20only%20for%20Jyoti%20to%20die%20in%20the%20clash%2C%20and%20Lalitesh%20to%20sustain%20serious%20injuries.%20The%20couple%20had%20married%20just%20six%20months%20ago.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20dust%20settled%20on%20the%20ghastly%20scene%2C%20the%20details%20behind%20the%20attack%20began%20to%20unravel.%20According%20to%20the%20police%2C%20Bobby%20was%20released%20from%20the%20Gautam%20Buddha%20Nagar%20jail%20merely%2015%20days%20ago.%20He%20was%20romantically%20involved%20with%20Champa%20Devi%20whose%20affections%20had%20shifted%20towards%20another%20man%20named%20Ajay%20during%20Bobby's%20absence.%20Champa%20Devi's%20first%20husband%20is%20dead%20and%20his%20second%20husband%20is%20disabled%20and%20lives%20in%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnraged%20by%20Champa%20Devi's%20affair%20with%20another%20man%2C%20Bobby%20had%20first%20called%20Ajay%20and%20threatened%20him%20before%20paying%20the%20family%20a%20visit.%20He%20was%20accompanied%20by%20another%20man%20when%20he%20arrived%20at%20Champa%20Devi's%20residence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20Bobby's%20knife%20attack%2C%20with%20Jyoti%20and%20Lalitesh%20tussling%20with%20him%2C%20Champa%20Devi%20dashed%20for%20the%20police%20station%20near%20her%20