20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESanya%20Malhotra's%20serene%20beauty%20captivates%20hearts...%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Haryana%20Numbers%20Stack%20Up%2C%20And%20How%20Chautala%20Family%20Math%20May%20Hold%20The%20Key%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20dramatic%20developments%20have%20reduced%20the%20BJP-led%20state%20government%20to%20a%20minority%20in%20Haryana%20Assembly.%20The%20Congress%20is%20now%20racing%20against%20time%20to%20make%20the%20most%20of%20the%20situation%20and%20cobble%20together%20the%20numbers%20required%20to%20topple%20the%20Nayab%20Singh%20Saini%20government%20months%20before%20state%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBehind%20the%20crisis%20is%20the%20decision%20of%20three%20Independent%20MLAs%20to%20switch%20from%20the%20BJP%20camp%20to%20the%20Congress%20side%20last%20evening.%20MLAs%20Sombir%20Sangwan%20(Dadri)%2C%20Randhir%20Singh%20Gollen%20(Pundri)%20and%20Dharampal%20Gonder%20(Nilokheri)%20announced%20their%20decision%20to%20withdraw%20support%20to%20the%20BJP%20government%20at%20a%20press%20meet%20in%20Rohtak%20yesterday.%20They%20were%20accompanied%20by%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Assembly%2C%20Congress's%20Bhupinder%20Singh%20Hooda%2C%20and%20state%20Congress%20chief%20Udai%20Bhan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20media%2C%20Mr%20Hooda%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20government%20should%20resign.%20President's%20rule%20should%20be%20imposed%20in%20the%20state%20and%20elections%20held.%20This%20is%20an%20anti-people%20government.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Saini%2C%20who%20took%20over%20the%20top%20post%20just%20about%20two%20months%20back%2C%20had%20a%20guarded%20response.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20heard%20about%20it%2C%20I%20knew%20that%20moment%20the%20Congress%20is%20trying%20to%20fulfil%20their%20wishes.%20Everyone%20has%20a%20wish.%20But%20the%20people%20know.%20They%20know%20the%20Congress%20has%20got%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20wishes%20of%20people%2C%20but%20is%20only%20focused%20on%20fulfilling%20their%20wishes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20The%20Chief%20Minister%20did%20not%20elaborate%20on%20how%20the%20BJP%20plans%20to%20counter%20the%20threat%20to%20its%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20significant%20remark%2C%20Haryana%20Speaker%20Gian%20Chand%20Gupta%20has%20said%20a%20majority%20test%20had%20earlier%20been%20conducted%20on%20the%20demand%20of%20Mr%20Hooda%20and%20there%20is%20no%20need%20to%20conduct%20another%20for%20six%20months.%20The%20Nayab%20Singh%20Saini%20government%20cleared%20a%20trust%20vote%20soon%20after%20he%20took%20over%20in%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20JJP%20Factor%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdding%20a%20twist%20to%20the%20Haryana%20political%20upheaval%2C%20the%20BJP's%20former%20ally%20Jannayak%20Janta%20Party%20(JJP)%20has%20offered%20support%20to%20the%20Congress.%20JJP%20leader%20and%20former%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Dushyant%20Chautala%20has%20said%20the%20government%20has%20lost%20the%20trust%20of%20the%20people.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20support%20a%20move%20to%20bring%20down%20the%20government.%20The%20Congress%20has%20to%20decide%20if%20it%20will%20make%20a%20move%20or%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20This%20comes%20less%20than%20two%20months%20after%20the%20BJP%20parted%20ways%20with%20JJP%2C%20which%20has%2010%20MLAs%2C%20and%20cobbled%20together%20enough%20numbers%20to%20cross%20the%20majority%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20The%20Numbers%20Stack%20Up%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2090-seat%20Haryana%20Assembly%20currently%20has%2088%20members.%20This%20means%20the%20majority%20mark%20is%2045.%20The%20BJP%20has%2040%20MLAs%20of%20its%20own%20and%20is%20supported%20by%20three%20out%20of%206%20Independent%20MLAs.%20This%20makes%20it%2043%2C%20two%20short%20of%20the%2