y%20smart%20with%20their%20bowling%20at%20the%20back-end%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sangakkara%20in%20the%20post-match%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20on%2C%20Samson%20was%20fined%2030%20per%20cent%20of%20his%20match%20fees%20for%20a%20Level%201%20offence%20under%20Article%202.8%20of%20the%20IPL's%20Code%20of%20Conduct%2C%20which%20talks%20about%20showing%20dissent%20at%20a%20decision%20made%20by%20the%20umpires.%20%E2%80%9COn-field%20umpires%20have%20to%20go%20by%20what%20TV%20umpire%20say.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20all%20the%20players%20have%20to%20abide%20by%20it.%20There's%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%20out%20in%20the%20middle%20on%20players%20and%20officials%2C%20so%20we%20try%20to%20sort%20it%20out%20the%20best%20way%20we%20can%2C%E2%80%9D%20added%20Sangakkara.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Pravin%20Amre%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F39999-pravin-kalyan-amre-playerprofile%5C%22%3EPravin%20Amre%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20DC%20assistant%20coach%2C%20praised%20Hope's%20athletic%20effort%20at%20the%20deep%20to%20take%20Samson's%20catch.%20%26quot%3BIn%20IPL%2C%20some%20momentums%20are%20very%20crucial%20and%20it%20was%20a%20decider%20moment%20in%20the%20game.%20Sanju%20was%20batting%20so%20well%20in%20the%20game%20and%20we%20have%20to%20give%20credit%20to%20the%20way%20Hope%20judged%20and%20balanced%20for%20the%20catch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlus%2C%20umpires%20are%20there%2C%20so%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20technology%2C%20and%20their%20decision%20is%20the%20final%20decision.%20I%20will%20give%20credit%20to%20Hope%20as%20it%20wasn't%20an%20easy%20catch.%20I%20spoke%20to%20him%20after%20the%20game%20and%20he%20said%20he%20anticipated%20it%20as%20the%20ball%20came%20very%2C%20very%20fast%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20471%20runs%20in%2011%20matches%2C%20Samson%20has%20been%20consistently%20amongst%20the%20runs%20for%20RR%2C%20including%20hitting%20five%20half-centuries%2C%20to%20be%20at%20third%20place%20in%20the%20Orange%20cap%20race.%20Amassing%20runs%20at%20a%20consistent%20rate%20was%20broadly%20identified%20as%20an%20issue%20with%20Samson%20in%20past%20seasons%2C%20something%20which%20is%20on%20display%20this%20season%2C%20apart%20from%20not%20being%20dismissed%20by%20spin%20and%20more%20importantly%2C%20upping%20his%20strike-rate%20whenever%20needed%2C%20as%20said%20by%20Sangakkara.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20biggest%20thing%20about%20this%20season%20for%20Sanju%20is%2C%20he's%20having%20a%20lot%20of%20clarity%20about%20the%20way%20he%20should%20bat.%20There%20are%20certain%20stages%20of%20the%20game%20that%20he%20seems%20to%20lose%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20concentration%2C%20which%20we've%20addressed%20from%20past%20seasons.%20He's%20really%20bought%20into%20it%20and%20into%20his%20role%2C%20not%20just%20as%20a%20captain%20but%20also%20when%20he%20bats%20just%20as%20a%20batter.%20(He's)%20kind%20of%20changed%20his%20mindset%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20rest%20and%20recovery%2C%20rather%20than%20just%20training%20all%20the%20time%20and%20being%20tired%20mentally%20and%20physically.%20So%20he's%20really%20enjoying%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20rest%20is%20just%20his%20exceptional%20ability.%20He's%20a%20very%20special%20player%20and%20when%20he%20is%20fresh%20and%20focused%2C%20there's%20nothing%20that%20he%20really%20can't%20do.%20I%20think%20his%20qualities%20are%20exceptional.%20He%20is%20a%20very%20humble%2C%20grounded%20guy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20much%20on%20social%20media%2C%20he%20likes%20his%20privacy.%20He%20really%20cares%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20group.%20So%20those%20are%20great%20qualities%20to%20have%20apart%20from%20his%20talent%20and%20skill.%20So%2C%20I%20think%2C%20he'd%20be%20exceptional%20in%20that%20group%20going%20into%20the%20World%20Cup.%20Again%2C%20he's%20just%20exceptionally%20talented%20against%20both%20pace%20and%20spin.%20High%20pace%20doesn't%20