nd%20a%20World%20Cup%20medal.%20He%20really%20deserves%20it.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYuvraj%20Singh%20who%20wishes%20to%20see%20his%20%26quot%3Bclose%20friend%26quot%3B%20win%20the%20elusive%20T20%20World%20Cup%20next%20month.%3Cbr%3E%5CnBesides%20reaching%20the%20final%20of%20the%2050-over%20World%20Cup%20and%20the%20WTC%20Final%20last%20year%2C%20India%20made%20the%20semifinals%20of%20the%202022%20T20%20World%20Cup%20under%20Rohit's%20captaincy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opener%20is%20set%20to%20lead%20the%20'Men%20in%20Blue'%20once%20again%20at%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20in%20the%20Caribbean%20and%20USA%2C%20starting%20on%20June%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B(Rohit's%20presence%20is%20going%20to%20be)%20very%20crucial.%20I%20think%20we%20need%20a%20really%20good%20captain%2C%20a%20sensible%20captain%20who%20takes%20decisions%20well%20under%20pressure.%20And%20he's%20the%20one%20to%20take%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Yuvraj%2C%20who%20is%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20ambassador%2C%20told%20ICC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Cup%202023%20final%20loss%20to%20Australia%20saw%20India's%20quest%20for%20an%20ICC%20title%20stretch%20to%2010%20years%20with%20their%20last%20victory%20dating%20back%20to%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20in%202013%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Mahendra%20Singh%20Dhoni.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYuvraj%20feels%20India%20needs%20someone%20with%20Rohit's%20expertise%20to%20lead%20the%20Indian%20team%20at%20the%20marquee%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20the%20captain%20when%20we%20lost%20in%20the%20(Cricket%20World%20Cup)%2050-over%20final%20(in%202023).%20He%20has%20won%20five%20IPL%20trophies%20as%20a%20captain.%20I%20think%20we%20need%20somebody%20like%20him%20to%20captain%20India.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715148300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fvvh7tl9g_rohit-sharma-pc-afp_625x300_03_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22htt