e%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20continues%20to%20enjoy%20tremendous%20goodwill%20in%20the%20state%2C%20but%20chances%20are%20that%20the%20'Modi%20factor'%20alone%20may%20not%20be%20enough%20for%20the%20party%20this%20time.%20Notably%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fharyana-chief-minister-nayab-singh-saini-measured-response-on-threat-to-government-5611470%5C%22%3Ethree%20independents%20withdrew%20their%20support%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20Saini%20government%20yesterday%20and%20have%20now%20switched%20to%20the%20Congress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Method%20To%20Congress%20List%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Congress%20has%20its%20own%20challenges.%20It%20finalised%20its%20list%20of%20Haryana%20candidates%20last%20week%20with%20the%20appointment%20of%20Raj%20Babbar%20as%20its%20nominee%20from%20Gurgaon.%20But%20the%20announcement%20has%20only%20exacerbated%20the%20fissures%20in%20the%20party's%20ranks.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fformer-haryana-chief-minister-bhupinder-singh-hooda%5C%22%3EBhupinder%20Singh%20Hooda%3C%2Fa%3E%20camp%20seems%20to%20have%20gotten%20its%20way%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20selection%20of%20candidates%2C%20while%20the%20other%20faction%20-%20comprising%20Selja%20Kumari%2C%20Randeep%20Singh%20Surjewala%20and%20Kiran%20Choudhry%20-%20has%20been%20left%20seething.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20that%20assembly%20polls%20in%20the%20state%20will%20come%20close%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20the%20Congress%20high%20command%20appears%20keen%20to%20keep%20Hooda%20in%20good%20humour%2C%20who%20has%20emerged%20as%20the%20tallest%20Jat%20leader%20in%20the%20state%20over%20the%20last%20decade.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sidelining%20of%20Brijendra%20Singh%20in%20Hisar%20apart%2C%20there%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20method%20to%20the%20Congress%20list%20as%20there%20is%20a%20conscious%20effort%20not%20to%20turn%20the%20election%20into%20a%20'Jat%20vs%20non-Jat'%20contest%20-%20as%20the%20BJP%20would%20like%20to%20have%20it.%20For%20instance%2C%20unlike%202019%2C%20when%20the%20Congress%20candidates%20list%20comprised%20four%20Jat%20names%2C%20this%20year's%20roster%20has%20only%20two%20names%20from%20the%20community.%20Care%20has%20also%20been%20taken%20to%20appeal%20more%20to%20urban%20voters%20and%20to%20have%20two%20Punjabis%20as%20well%20as%20a%20Brahmin%20in%20Sonipat.%20The%20strategy%20is%20clearly%20aimed%20at%20denting%20the%20BJP's%20appeal%20among%20these%20communities%20in%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-danger-bjp-vs-congress-after-3-independents-quit-in-haryana-5612422%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0%26quot%3BNo%20Danger%26quot%3B%3A%20BJP%20vs%20Congress%20After%203%20Independents%20Quit%20In%20Haryana%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20Babbar's%20candidacy%2C%20Sonipat's%20Satpal%20Brahmachari%20and%20Karnal's%20Divyanshu%20Budhiraja%20(the%2031-year-old%20Haryana%20Youth%20Congress%20president)%20have%20also%20come%20as%20surprise%20picks.%20In%20a%20nutshell%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20struck%20a%20deft%20balancing%20act%20by%20giving%20tickets%20to%20two%20Dalits%2C%20two%20Jats%20and%20two%20Punjabis%2C%20and%20one%20each%20to%20a%20Gujjar%2C%20an%20Ahir%20and%20a%20Brahmin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EJindal's%20Candidature%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20ceded%20the%20Kurukshetra%20seat%20to%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20-%20where%20state%20chief%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Sushil%20Gupta's%20name%20was%20announced%20before%20the%20naming%20of%20Congress%20candidates%20-%20there%20is%20also%20an%20Agarwal%20on%20the%20INDIA%20bloc's%20list.%20The%20perception%20is%20that%20the%20BJP%20admitted%20Congress%20turncoat%20Navin%20Jindal%20as%20a%20direct%20response%20to%20Gupta's%20candidature.%20Apart%20from%20being%20from%20the%20same%20community%2C%20the%20two%20are%20also%20the%20richest%20candidates%20in%20the%20fray%20and%20have%20their%20business%20empires%20spread%20across%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20another%20factor%20at%20play%20here%2C%20and%20that%20has%20to%20do%20with%20the%20arrest%20of%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal.%20The%20embattled%20AAP%20convenor%20is%20himself%20an%20Agarwal%20from%20Haryana%2C%20and%20the%20community%20-%20which%20accounts%20for%20over%204%25%20of%20the%20state's%20population%20-%20has%20warmed%20up%20to%20him%20in%20recent%20times.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20hence%2C%20Jindal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%20Surrendered%20to%20Hoodas%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20only%20common%20sense%20not%20to%20put%20all%20your%20eggs%20in%20one%20basket.%20However%2C%20the%20Congress%20seems%20to%20have%20done%20exactly%20that%20in%20Haryana.%20Among%20its%20nine%20candidates%2C%20Selja%20Kumari%2C%20fielded%20from%20Sirsa%2C%20is%20the%20only%20one%20who%20is%20not%20from%20the%20Hooda%20camp%3B%20Ambala%20candidate%20Varun%20Chaudhary%2C%20son%20of%20veteran%20leader%20Phool%20Chand%20Mulana%2C%20is%20acceptable%20to%20all%20factions%20and%20thus%20is%20not%20really%20a%20Hooda%20nominee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20has%20Hooda%20managed%20to%20get%20all%20his%20loyalists%20on%20the%20list%2C%20but%20he%20also%20ensured%20that%20Brijendra%20Singh%2C%20son%20of%20veteran%20politician%20Birender%20Singh%2C%20was%20denied%20a%20ticket.%20Ironically%2C%20it%20was%20Singh's%20move%20to%20the%20Congress%20from%20the%20BJP%20that%20actually%20helped%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20turn%20the%20tide%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20polls.%20He%20is%20a%20winnable%20candidate%20and%20a%20sitting%20MP%2C%20but%20Hooda's%20grudge%20seems%20to%20have%20weighed%20against%20him.%20That%20grudge%20goes%20back%20years.%20Once%20bitter%20rivals%20in%20the%20Congress%2C%20it%20was%20on%20account%20of%20Hooda's%20resistance%20that%20Birender%20Singh%20was%20denied%20a%20berth%20in%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh%20Cabinet%20in%202013%20after%20being%20invited%20to%20the%20swearing-in.%20The%20incident%20ultimately%20led%20to%20his%20exit%20from%20the%20Congress%20a%20year%20later.%20Now%2C%20with%20the%20denial%20of%20a%20ticket%20to%20Brijendra%2C%20Hooda%20seems%20intent%20on%20clearing%20the%20way%20for%20his%20own%20son%2C%20Deepinder%20Hooda%2C%20to%20take%20over%20as%20the%20undisputed%20Jat%20leader%20in%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fharyana-will-bjps-experiment-with-a-non-jat-chief-minister-nayab-singh-saini-pay-off-5231949%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%20Opinion%3A%20Will%20BJP's%20Experiment%20With%20A%20Non-Jat%20Chief%20Minister%20In%20Haryana%20Pay%20Off%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20just%20senior%20Hooda%2C%20even%20the%20junior%20Hooda%20managed%20to%20get%20one%20of%20his%20loyalists%20-%20the%20young%20Budhiraja%20-%20on%20the%20Congress%20list.%20Given%20that%20he%20will%20be%20facing%20off%20against%20Khattar%2C%20the%20decision%20has%20not%20gone%20down%20well%20with%20a%20few%20others%20who%20were%20eyeing%20the%20seat%2C%20including%20Chanakya%20Pandit%2C%20son%20of%20former%20assembly%20speaker%20Kuldeep%20Sharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Missing%20Lal%20Clans%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20Hooda%20wanted%20to%20deny%20Brijendra%20Singh%20his%20due%2C%20there%20could%20have%20been%20a%20more%20honourable%20way%20of%20doing%20so.%20For%20instance%2C%20Congress%20could%20have%20fielded%20former%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Chander%20Mohan%2C%20son%20of%20Bhajan%20Lal%2C%20as%20a%20surprise%20pick.%20This%20could%20have%20been%20dubbed%20as%20a%20way%20to%20get%20the%20backing%20of%20the%20sulking%20Kuldeep%20Bishnoi%20-%20the%20younger%20brother%20of%20Chander%20Mohan%20-%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Bishnoi%20community%20as%20a%20whole.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBishnoi%2C%20who%20has%20been%20sidelined%20in%20the%20BJP%20lately%2C%20was%20denied%20the%20Hisar%20seat.%20In%20such%20a%20scenario%2C%20the%20Congress%20could%20have%20fielded%20a%20second%20Jat%20leader%20in%20Karan%20Singh%20Dalal%20from%20Faridabad%20(instead%20of%20Mahendar%20Pratap%20Singh).%20The%20result%20is%20that%20Dalal%20is%20now%20miffed%20and%20has%20been%20in%20revolt%20mode%20since%20Hooda%20had%20purportedly%20assured%20him%20of%20a%20ticket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOr%2C%20Shruti%20Choudhry%2C%20granddaughter%20of%20Bansi%20Lal%2C%20could%20have%20been%20retained%20from%20the%20Bhiwani-Mahendragarh%20seat%20as%20a%20second%20Jat%20candidate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20there%20is%20no%20representation%20this%20time%20from%20two%20Lal%20clans%20-%20Bhajan%20Lal%20and%20Bansi%20Lal%20-%20although%20there%20are%20many%20names%20from%20the%20Devi%20Lal%20clan%20on%20the%20Indian%20National%20Lok%20Dal%20(INLD)%2C%20the%20JJP%20and%20the%20BJP%20lists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP's%20Strategy%3B%20Survival%20Question%20For%20JJP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20decision%20to%20replace%20Khattar%20with%20Saini%20was%20an%20admission%20that%20the%20state%20government%20might%20not%20have%20been%20as%20popular%20in%20its%20second%20term.%20The%20party%20is%20hoping%20that%20after%20its%20split%20with%20the%20Dushyant%20Chautala-led%20JJP%2C%20the%20anti-incumbency%20factor%20will%20be%20somewhat%20neutralised.%20The%20JJP%2C%20in%20any%20case%2C%20unravelled%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20days%20once%20it%20lost%20power%2C%20with%20even%20its%20state%20president%20deserting%20it%2C%20along%20with%20a%20number%20of%20prominent%20leaders.%20The%20JJP's%20Ajay%20Chautala%20did%20try%20to%20extend%20an%20olive%20branch%20to%20its%20parent%20party%2C%20the%20INLD%2C%20urging%20it%20to%20bury%20the%20hatchet%2C%20but%20in%20vain.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20list%20doesn't%20have%20too%20many%20surprises.%20Apart%20from%20Jindal%2C%20it%20has%20two%20more%20Congress%20turncoats%20this%20time%3A%20Ashok%20Tanwar%20from%20Sirsa%20and%20Ranjit%20Singh%20Chautala%20from%20the%20Devi%20Lal%20clan.%20Chautala%20was%20nominated%20from%20Hisar%20just%20days%20after%20he%20joined%20the%20BJP.%20That%20would%20mean%20that%20out%20of%20the%20BJP's%2010%20candidates%2C%20only%20four%20are%20originally%20from%20its%20own%20stock.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20believes%20it%20has%20a%20good%20chance%20to%20net%20a%20few%20seats%20in%20the%20state%2C%20while%20the%20BJP%20reckons%20that%20the%20leads%20it%20secured%20in%202014%20and%202019%20would%20be%20difficult%20to%20bridge.%20If%20the%20former%20puts%20its%20drubbing%20in%202014%20and%202019%20down%20to%20the%20Modi%20wave%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20hoping%20that%20the%20same%20factor%20will%20help%20it%20in%20this%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20as%20well.%C2%A0There%20may%20be%20many%20variables%20at%20play%2C%20but%20one%20thing%20is%20certain%3A%20Haryana%20is%20poised%20to%20witness%20a%20keen%20contest%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Anand%20Kochukudy%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20and%20columnist.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715148180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2F4rqldqeg_congress-generic_625x300_18_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fharyana-bjp-tries-to-retain-lead-under-saini-while-congress-tackles-infighting-5615125%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress%20believes%20it%20has%20a%20good%20chance%20to%20net%20a%20few%20seats%20in%20Haryana%2C%20while%20the%20BJP%20reckons%20that%20the%20leads%20it%20secured%20in%202014%20and%202019%20would%20be%20difficult%20to%20bridge.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fharyana-bjp-tries-to-retain-lead-under-sain