2%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fnicholas-galitzine-to-ranbir-kapoor-actors-who-romanced-older-actresses-on-screen%2Fphotostory%2F109937662.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F109937662.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EFro%20Nicholas%20Galitzine%20romancing%20Anne%20Hathaway%20in%20'The%20Idea%20Of%20You'%20to%20Ranbir%20Kapoor%20steaming%20up%20the%20screens%20with%20Aishwarya%20Rai%20Bachchan%2C%20here's%20a%20list%20of%20actors%20who%20romanced%20older%20actresses%20on-screen.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20BJP%20Leader%20Called%20Him%20%26quot%3BGandhis'%20Chaprasi%26quot%3B%2C%20Congress's%20Amethi%20Pick%20Replies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGearing%20for%20his%20big%20poll%20fight%20against%20Union%20Minister%20Smriti%20Irani%20in%20Amethi%2C%20Congress%20candidate%20Kishori%20Lal%20Sharma%20said%20he%20still%20wants%20party%20leaders%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20or%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20to%20contest%20from%20the%20prestige%20seat%20as%20it%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bpart%20of%20their%20legacy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20campaign%20trail%20for%20the%20May%2020%20election%2C%20NDTV%20caught%20up%20with%20Mr%20Sharma%20for%20a%20chat.%20Mr%20Sharma%20has%20served%20as%20an%20MP's%20representative%20in%20Amethi%20and%20Raebareli%20and%20has%20been%20closely%20linked%20with%20the%20Congress's%20poll%20campaigns%20there%20for%20about%20four%20decades.%20Asked%20how%20it%20was%20different%20this%20time%2C%20he%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20the%20same%20as%20before.%20This%20time%2C%20the%20leadership%20has%20given%20me%20a%20different%20role%20and%20I%20am%20working%20accordingly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20his%20statement%20that%20he%20wanted%20Mr%20Gandhi%20to%20contest%20from%20Amethi%2C%20a%20seat%20his%20parents%20and%20uncle%20have%20represented%20in%20the%20past%2C%20Mr%20Sharma%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20still%20want%20that.%20If%20there%20is%20a%20possibility%2C%20I%20would%20still%20want%20Rahul%20ji%20or%20Priyanka%20ji%20to%20contest%20polls%20from%20there.%20This%20is%20a%20part%20of%20their%20legacy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmethi%20has%20been%20represented%20by%20Sanjay%20Gandhi%2C%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20and%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20in%20the%20past%20and%20was%20won%20by%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20thrice%20in%20a%20row%20before%20he%20was%20defeated%20by%20the%20BJP's%20Smriti%20Irani%20in%20the%202019%20election.%20Along%20with%20Raebareli%2C%20it%20is%20among%20the%20most-watched%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20primarily%20because%20they%20are%20Congress's%20prestige%20battles.%20Congress%20leader%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20is%20leading%20from%20the%20front%20and%20overseeing%20the%20party's%20campaign%20in%20these%20two%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20repeated%20Ms%20Irani%20as%20its%20candidate.%20The%20Union%20Minister%20has%20said%20the%20Gandhis'%20decision%20not%20to%20contest%20the%20seat%20shows%20that%20they%20have%20conceded%20defeat.%20BJP%20leaders%20have%20described%20Mr%20Sharma%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bproxy%20candidate%26quot%3B%2C%20with%20its%20Raebareli%20pick%20going%20so%20far%20as%20to%20call%20Mr%20Sharma%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20%26quot%3Bchaprasi%26quot%3B%20(peon).%C2%A0%26quot%3BIf%20he%20(Gandhi)%20wanted%20to%20win%20Amethi%2C%20would%20they%20give%20a%20ticket%20to%20his%20chaprasi%20(peon)%2C%26quot%3B%20BJP's%20Raebareli%20candidate%20and%20UP%20minister%20Dinesh%20Pratap%20Singh%20has%20said%20in%20an%20interview.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20BJP%20leader's%20remark%2C%20Mr%20Sharma%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BThese%20are%20their%20values%2C%20my%20father%20was%20illiterate%2C%20but%20he%20taught%20me%20good%20values.%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20comment%20on%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715145360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fdos5g038_kishori-lal-sharma_625x300_08_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-amethi-a-bjp-leader-called-him-gandhis-chaprasi-congresss-amethi-pick-replies-5614901%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gearing%20for%20his%20big%20poll%20fight%20against%20Union%20Minister%20Smriti%20Irani%20in%20Amethi%2C%20Congress%20candidate%20Kishori%20Lal%20Sharma%20said%20he%20still%20wants%20party%20leaders%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20or%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20to%20contest%20from%20the%20prestige%20seat%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-amethi-a-bjp-leader-called-him-gandhis-chaprasi-congresss-amethi-pick-replies-5614901%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-amethi-a-bjp-leader-called-him-gandhis-chaprasi-congresss-amethi-pick-replies-5614901%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-amethi-a-bjp-leader-called-him-gandhis-chaprasi-congresss-amethi-pick-replies-5614901%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Now%2C%20Punjab%20Congress%20chief%20calls%20Pulwama%20attack%20'mystery'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715145345000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109937316%2Cimgsize-24424.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fafter-channis-stuntbaazi-remark-punjab-congress-chief-calls-pulwama-attack-mystery%2Farticleshow%2F109936516.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Punjab%20Congress%20chief%20Amardiner%20Singh%20Raja%20Warring%20on%20Wednesday%20stoked%20a%20fresh%20controversy%20