m%2Fdonald-trump-hit-gag-violation-judge-threatens-jail-time-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehold%20him%20in%20contempt%20of%20court%20once%20again%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20understand%20that%20your%20client%20is%20upset%20at%20this%20point%2C%20but%20he%20is%20cursing%20audibly%2C%20and%20he%20is%20shaking%20his%20head%20visually%20and%20that's%20contemptuous%2C%26quot%3B%20Merchan%20told%20Trump's%20lawyer%20Todd%20Blanche.%20%26quot%3BIt%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20intimidate%20the%20witness%20and%20the%20jury%20can%20see%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDaniels%2C%20at%20that%20point%20in%20her%20testimony%2C%20had%20begun%20telling%20the%20story%20of%20going%20to%20the%20bathroom%20while%20meeting%20with%20Trump%20in%20his%20suite%20after%20a%20golf%20tournament%20in%20Lake%20Tahoe%2C%20California%20%E2%80%94%20which%20she%20later%20testified%20was%20a%20prelude%20to%20Trump%20having%20sex%20with%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221336%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22trump%20merchan%20cursing%20audibly%20transcript%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663ab8a9b4abc992e8c6c18f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22336%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDonald%20Trump%20was%20%26quot%3Bcursing%20audibly%26quot%3B%20during%20testimony%20from%20Stormy%20Daniels%2C%20according%20to%20New%20York%20Supreme%20Court%20Justice%20Juan%20Merchan.%3Cp%3ECourt%20trial%20transcript%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Manhattan%20district%20attorney's%20office%20alleges%20that%20Trump%20falsified%20business%20records%20to%20cover%20up%20a%20%24130%2C000%20hush-money%20payment%20to%20Daniels%20ahead%20of%20the%202016%20election%20to%20keep%20her%20silent%20about%20the%20sex%20%E2%80%94%20something%20Trump%20vehemently%20denies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20private%20sidebar%20conversation%2C%20which%20was%20included%20in%20the%20trial%20transcript%20Business%20Insider%20obtained%2C%20Merchan%20also%20criticized%20Trump's%20reaction%20to%20an%20anecdote%20Daniels%20gave%20about%20smacking%20him%20on%20the%20behind%20with%20a%20magazine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20conversation%20that%20evening%20in%20Trump's%20hotel%20room%2C%20the%20real%20estate%20mogul%20had%20bragged%20about%20being%20on%20the%20cover%20of%20a%20recent%20financial%20magazine%2C%20Daniels%20testified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20said%2C%20'Someone%20should%20spank%20you%20with%20that%2C'%26quot%3B%20Daniels%20testified.%20%26quot%3B'That's%20the%20only%20interest%20I%20have%20in%20that%20magazine.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20he%20thought%20I%20would%20do%20it.%20So%2C%20he%20rolled%20it%20up%20and%20gave%20me%20the%20look%20that%20he%20dared%20me%20to%20do%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Daniels%20continued.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20now%20I%20kind%20of%20had%20to.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUpon%20further%20prodding%20from%20prosecutor%20Susan%20Hoffinger%2C%20Daniels%20elaborated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20took%20it%20from%20him%20and%20said%2C%20turn%20around.%20And%20I%20swatted%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhere%20do%20you%20swat%20him%3F%26quot%3B%20Hoffinger%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRight%20on%20the%20butt%2C%26quot%3B%20Daniels%20testified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMerchan%2C%20in%20the%20sidebar%20conversation%2C%20said%20Trump%20reacted%20to%20that%20story%20inappropriately.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20time%20I%20noticed%20when%20Ms.%20Daniels%20was%20testifying%20about%20rolling%20up%20the%20magazine%2C%20and%20presumably%20smacking%20your%20client%2C%20and%20after%20that%20point%20he%20shook%20his%20head%20and%20he%20looked%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20Merchan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20also%20said%20Trump%20%26quot%3Buttered%20a%20vulgarity%26quot%3B%20when%20Daniels%20testified%20about%20%26quot%3BThe%20Apprentice.%26quot%3B%20Daniels%20had%20testified%20that%20Trump%20offered%20to%20have%20her%20on%20the%20NBC%20show%2C%20but%20that%20the%20promise%20never%20came%20to%20fruition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20he%20was%20looking%20at%20you%2C%20Mr.%20Blanche%2C%20later%20when%20we%20were%20talking%20about%20'The%20Apprentice%2C'%20at%20that%20point%20he%20again%20uttered%20a%20vulgarity%20and%20looked%20at%20you%20this%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Merchan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221348%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Merchan%20trump%20trial%20transcript%20magazine%20smacking%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663ab9259686a6f37bfd1519%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22272%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENew%20York%20Supreme%20Court%20Justice%20Juan%20Merchan%20said%20Trump%20reacted%20inappropriately%20when%20Stormy%20Daniels%20talked%20about%20%26quot%3Bsmacking%26quot%3B%20his%20behind%20with%20a%20rolled-up%20financial%20magazine.%3Cp%3ECourt%20trial%20transcript%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMerchan%20has%20previously%20issued%20a%20gag%20order%20preventing%20Trump%20from%20talking%20about%20witnesses%20or%20jurors%2C%20out%20of%20concern%20that%20they%20could%20be%20threatened.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%2C%20earlier%20this%20week%2C%20found%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-hit-gag-violation-judge-threatens-jail-time-2024-5%23%3A~%3Atext%3DJudge%2520Juan%2520Merchan%2520hit%2520Trump%2Cjail%2520sanction%252C%2522%2520he%2520said.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump%20violated%20the%20gag%20order%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20total%20of%2010%20times%20and%20threatened%20to%20jail%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20appears%20that%20the%20%241%2C000%20fines%20are%20not%20serving%20as%20a%20deterrent%3B%20therefore%2C%20going%20forward%2C%20this%20Court%20will%20have%20to%20consider%20a%20jail%20sanction%20if%20recommended%2C%26quot%3B%20Merchan%20told%20Trump%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20the%20first%20time%20Trump%20has%20acted%20out%20in%20court%20wh