02015.%20Following%20his%20departure%2C%20Schmidt%20has%20invested%20in%20various%20AI%20companies%2C%20including%20Anthropic.%20He%20also%20became%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Defense's%20Innovation%20Board%20in%202016%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nscai.gov%2F2021%2F09%2F23%2Fnscai-to-sunset-in-october%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Echaired%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20National%20Security%20Commission%20on%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20for%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchmidt%20said%20the%20US%20stands%20to%20be%20the%20clear%20winner%20in%20the%20AI%20race%20%E2%80%94%20as%20long%20as%20it%20doesn't%20screw%20up%20its%20lead.%20Since%20China%20is%20focused%20on%20dominating%20certain%20industries%2C%20the%20US%20needs%20to%20compete%20with%20them%20and%20win%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinese-government-approves-more-ai-models-rivals-us-report-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAt%20the%20start%20of%202024%2C%20China%20had%20approved%20over%2040%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20models%20in%20a%20six-month%20period%2C%20including%2014%20new%20Large%20Language%20Models%20approved%20for%20public%20use%20in%20a%20week%20span.%20Baidu%2C%20a%20search%20engine%20giant%20referred%20to%20as%20%26quot%3BChina's%20Google%2C%26quot%3B%20is%20leading%20the%20pack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchmidt%20talked%20about%20four%20factors%20that%20contributed%20to%20his%20view%20that%20China%20is%20behind%20in%20the%20AI%20arms%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ae9c3877-765e-45a6-b550-e09977fe192f%5C%22%3EChip%20shortages%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESchmidt%20said%20China%20is%20%26quot%3Bstruggling%20because%20of%20chips%26quot%3B%20and%20shortages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20separate%20interview%20with%20CNBC%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Schmidt%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2Fvideo%2F2024%2F05%2F07%2Fwatch-cnbcas-full-interview-with-former-google-executive-chairman-and-ceo-eric-schmidt.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20China%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20set%20back%20by%20the%20Trump%20and%20Biden%20administrations%20restricting%20access%20to%20high-speed%20chips%2C%20particularly%20Nvidia%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20certainly%20angry%20about%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Schmidt%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chips%20serve%20as%20a%20crucial%20component%20in%20the%20effort%20to%20scale%20AI.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-china-tech-cold-war-everything-that-has-happened-2019-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etech-related%20tensions%20between%20the%20US%20and%20China%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20resulted%20in%20a%20push%20from%20the%20government%20to%20produce%20semiconductors%20in%20the%20US.%20In%20November%202023%2C%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Commerce%20implemented%20the%20Advanced%20Computing%20Chips%20Rule%20making%20it%20harder%20for%20China%20to%20import%20advanced%20AI%20chips%20from%20American%20manufacturers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-is-firing-back-again-in-china-chip-semiconductor-wars-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBiden%20administration%20most%20recently%20considered%3C%2Fa%3E%20imposing%20sanctions%20on%20several%20Chinese%20semiconductor%20firms%20linked%20to%20Huawei%20in%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fa88c71d-9aa6-4299-a800-6c2e77fd1503%5C%22%3ESchmidt%20thinks%20there's%20less%20Chinese%20material%20to%20train%20AI%20models%20with%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESchmidt%20also%20said%20in%20the%20CNBC%20interview%20that%20there's%20not%20as%20much%20Chinese%20material%20available%20to%20train%20large%20language%20models.%20Since%20English%20dominates%20the%20internet%2C%20research%20papers%2C%20and%20books%20that%20large%20language%20models%20train%20on%2C%20he%20believes%20English%20provides%20a%20larger%20pool%20of%20information%20to%20learn%20from.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3EThat's%20why%20English%20is%20so%20strong%20in%20these%20large%20language%20models%2C%26quot%3B%20Schmidt%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20most%20training%20data%20is%20in%20English%2C%20he%20said%2C%20which%20could%20lead%20to%20misunderstandings%20and%20misinterpretations%20in%20other%20languages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222484e2d7-9093-498d-911e-b936e01842bd%5C%22%3EReduced%20funding%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESchmidt%20said%20that%20China%20is%20also%20facing%20a%20huge%20reduction%20in%20foreign%20investment%20and%20at-risk%20venture%20capital.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20US%20has%20exploded%20in%20these%20areas%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-shrinking-xi-jinping-debt-real-estate-american-world-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChina%20has%20been%20on%20the%20economic%20decline%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%20and%20it%20continues%20to%20face%20deflation%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20November%202023%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-foreign-investment-deficit-beijing-xi-jinping-zero-covid-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eit%20suffered%20its%20first%20investment%20deficit%20as%20US%20%3C%2Fa%3Etensions%20rose%20and%20Western%20countries%20leaned%20away%20from%20business%20involvement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a1e08c85-719b-468e-9aaa-5f0d190e3ff8%5C%22%3EFocusing%20on%20the%20wrong%20areas%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Google%20CEO%20said%20that%20China%20is%20focused%20on%20building%20for-profit%20application%20companies%20which%20may%20ultimately%20be%20successful.%20But%20they're%20not%20platform-focused%2C%20he%20argued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThree%20or%20four%20of%20the%20top%20apps%20in%20America%20are%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20of%20Chinese%20origin%2C%26quot%3B%20Schmidt%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20the%20leader