e%20to%20join%20Meghan%20on%20a%20visit%20to%20Nigeria.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarry's%20relationship%20with%20his%20father%20has%20been%20strained%20by%20his%20revelations%20and%20criticisms%20of%20royal%20life%20aired%20in%20a%20television%20interview%2C%20a%20Netflix%20documentary%20and%20his%20autobiography%20%26quot%3BSpare%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2039-year-old%20prince%20was%20filmed%20leaving%20his%20car%20as%20he%20attended%20a%20London%20event%20to%20mark%20the%2010th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20Invictus%20Games%20he%20launched%20to%20support%20wounded%20service%20personnel%20and%20veterans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20was%20just%20three%20miles%20(five%20kilometres)%20from%2075-year-old%20Charles's%20Clarence%20House%20residence%20in%20central%20London.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECharles%20has%20been%20undergoing%20treatment%20for%20an%20unspecified%20cancer%20and%20recently%20resumed%20public%20engagements%20after%20doctors%20said%20they%20were%20%26quot%3Bvery%20encouraged%26quot%3B%20by%20his%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20suspended%20public%20engagements%20after%20his%20diagnosis%20but%20continued%20official%20work%20in%20private%2C%20including%20receiving%20foreign%20diplomats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715102280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F4i59bj68_king-charles_625x300_30_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fprince-harry-in-uk-for-events-but-will-not-meet-father-king-charles-5611721%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prince%20Harry%20arrived%20in%20the%20UK%20on%20Tuesday%20for%20events%20marking%20the%20anniversary%20of%20his%20Invictus%20Games%20but%20will%20not%20meet%20his%20father%20King%20Charles%20III%2C%20who%20is%20undergoing%20cancer%20treatment%2C%20according%20to%20his%