tle%20against%20tuberculosis%3C%2Fa%3E%20(TB)%20that%20the%20community%20was%20fighting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20were%20dying%20in%20front%20of%20our%20eyes%2C%E2%80%9D%20Wohab%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20often%20started%20with%20a%20cough%20and%20before%20the%20person%20knew%20it%2C%20they%20were%20detected%20with%20TB.%20As%20we%20spoke%20to%20people%20in%20the%20neighbourhood%2C%20we%20understood%20that%20almost%2050%20percent%20of%20people%20with%20chest%20problems%20did%20not%20go%20for%20a%20checkup%20until%20they%20started%20vomiting%20blood.%20And%20once%20they%20reached%20this%20stage%2C%20it%20was%2C%20more%20often%20than%20not%2C%20too%20late.%20We%20also%20found%20that%20there%20were%20only%20three%20doctors%20in%20the%20Sundarbans%20at%20that%20time%20and%20more%20than%20three%20lakh%20patients.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20wanted%20to%20help.%20They%20had%20heard%20about%20doctors%20in%20Kolkata%20who%20were%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F259846%2Fdoctors-couple-covid-relief-free-medicine-collection-underprivileged-shell%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edistributing%20medicines%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20free.%20%E2%80%9CSabitri%20and%20I%20started%20making%20trips%20to%20these%20clinics%20to%20collect%20the%20medicine%20samples%20which%20we%20distributed%20in%20a%20small%20room%20that%20a%20tea%20shop%20owner%20had%20lent%20to%20us.%20Through%20the%20weeks%2C%20people%20from%20across%20Sundarban%20islands%20would%20come%20to%20get%20an%20antidote%20to%20tuberculosis%2C%20cold%2C%20cough%20and%20fever.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-23-at-10.53.09-AM-1714724989.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mohammed%20Abdul%2