0They%20also%20have%20a%20centre%20where%20girls%20are%20taught%20and%20helped%20to%20complete%20their%20school%20and%20college%20education.%20%E2%80%9COver%20700%20children%20have%20been%20helped%20in%20total%20and%20many%20of%20them%20have%20secured%20Government%20jobs%2C%E2%80%9D%20Wohab%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20educational%20endeavours%20are%20based%20on%20the%20belief%20that%20the%20youth%20of%20the%20Sundarbans%20are%20bubbling%20with%20creativity%20that%20mustn%E2%80%99t%20be%20stifled.%20These%20programmes%20are%20a%20step%20towards%20helping%20these%20children%20to%20channel%20their%20talents%20in%20a%20constructive%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20time%20the%20couple%20has%20encountered%20adversity%20%E2%80%94%20sometimes%20with%20diminishing%20funds%2C%20other%20times%20with%20the%20climate%20playing%20spoilsport%20%E2%80%94%20they%20are%20reminded%20of%20why%20they%20started.%20From%20a%20humble%20initiative%20in%20a%20tea%20shop%2C%20the%20foundation%20has%20evolved%20into%20a%20place%20where%20new%20possibilities%20are%20given%20space%20to%20grow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%E2%80%99d%20like%20to%20support%20them%20with%20funds%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shisindia.org%2Fsupportus%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere%E2%80%99s%20a%20link%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20with%20the%20details.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715003816000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-22-at-10.31.59-AM-1714724688.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D348884%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20SHIS%20Foundation%2C%20founded%20by%20Mohammed%20Abdul%20Wohab%20and%20Sabitri%20Pal%2C%20operates%20in%20the%20Sundarbans%2C%20West%20Beng