n%3Cp%3EThe%20department%20has%20issued%20a%20warning%20for%20hotter%20temperatures%20across%20several%20states%20in%20the%20coming%20weeks.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20temperatures%20have%20soared%20between%2040%20to%2045%20degrees%20Celsius%20in%20parts%20of%20Odisha%20earlier%20this%20week.%20Similar%20conditions%20have%20been%20observed%20in%20Gangetic%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20Vidarbha%2C%20and%20southwestern%20parts%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20among%20other%20regions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERising%20temperatures%20lead%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20the%20use%20of%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F281434%2Fagra-data-scientist-builds-solar-power-eco-friendly-air-conditioner-exalta%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20air%20conditioners%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20electricity%20as%20people%20try%20to%20escape%20the%20heat.%20%E2%80%9CWorking%20from%20home%20becomes%20more%20challenging%20as%20the%20temperature%20starts%20to%20rise%20as%20early%20as%207%20am.%20Living%20in%20apartments%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20allow%20us%20much%20room%20to%20naturally%20cool%20the%20space%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vinaya%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20situation%20may%20seem%20bleak%2C%20architects%20and%20designers%20suggest%2C%20depending%20on%20your%20geography%2C%20a%20few%20steps%20to%20keep%20your%20home%20naturally%20cool.%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20spoke%20with%20several%20experts%20to%20learn%20about%20the%20secrets%20of%20designing%20a%20%E2%80%98cool%E2%80%99%20house.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGoing%20Back%20To%20Your%20Roots%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20look%20back%20at%20the%20houses%20that%20our%20ancestors%20built%2C%20the%20structures%20with%20open%20spaces%2C%20inward-looking%20homes%20with%20courtyards%20and%20huge%20windows%20helped%20to%20keep%20the%20home%20naturally%20cool.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamira%20Rathod%2C%20an%20architect%20and%20designer%2C%20applied%20similar%20techniques%20to%20make%20a%20%E2%80%9CCool%20House%E2%80%9D%20located%20in%20Gujarat.%20The%20architect%20decided%20to%20utilise%20the%20wind%2C%20design%20and%20cooling%20materials%20to%20build%20and%20cool%20down%20the%20house.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20architect%20suggests%20using%20the%20wind%20in%20a%20way%20that%20it%20travels%20through%20the%20home%20making%20it%20cooler.%20For%20the%20cool%20house%20located%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20she%20used%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctrack-like%20design%20with%20rooms%20on%20either%20side%20of%20the%20house%20with%20a%20courtyard%20to%20help%20the%20wind%20circulate.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201067px)%20100vw%2C%201067px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F71e1f2ce8e654135b509da9fba6c6619_311592766_142412935197808_3738696823372802622_n-1680175563.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221067%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Going%20back%20to%20traditional%20designs%20and%20making%20use%20of%20natural%20materials%20to%20build%20a%20naturally%20cool%20house.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F71e1f2ce8e654135b509da9fba6c6619_311592766_142412935197808_3738696823372802622_n-1680175563.jpg%201067w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F71e1f2ce8e654135b509da9fba6c6619_311592766_142412935197808_3738696823372802622_n-1680175563-240x300.jpg%20240w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F71e1f2ce8e654135b509da9fba6c6619_311592766_142412935197808_3738696823372802622_n-1680175563-500x625.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F71e1f2ce8e654135b509da9fba6c6619_311592766_142412935197808_3738696823372802622_n-1680175563-768x959.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F71e1f2ce8e654135b509da9fba6c6619_311592766_142412935197808_3738696823372802622_n-1680175563-150x187.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-313970%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGoing%20back%20to%20traditional%20designs%20and%20making%20use%20of%20natural%20materials%20to%20build%20a%20naturally%20cool%20house.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Instagram%3A%20Sketch%20Design%20Studio%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEvaporative%20cooling%20for%20your%20home%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShipra%20Singhania%2C%20the%20principal%20designer%20of%20Sketch%20Design%20Studio%2C%20created%20her%20home%20alongside%20her%20mother%20using%20neem%2C%20jaggery%20and%20methi.%20The%20house%20uses%20a%20thatch%20roof%20to%20keep%20t%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330088%2Fkerala-architect-designer-anupa-kurian-renovates-century-old-ancestral-home-sustainable-upcycle%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20house%20breathable%20and%20cooler%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20summer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20always%20a%20good%20idea%20to%20look%20back%20at%20our%20ancestors%20and%20how%20they%20used%20various%20techniques%20to%20deal%20with%20indoor%20heat.%20Evaporative%20cooling%20is%20a%20technique%20where%20you%20build%20an%20indoor%20water%20body%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20say%20a%20fountain%20to%20cool%20down%20the%20temperature%20inside%20the%20house%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20water%20body%20in%20the%20house%20can%20do%20wonders.%20Additionally%2C%20it%20can%20also%20cool%20down%20the%20air%20that%20passes%20through%20the%20home.%20This%20method%20is%20very%20effective%20in%20homes%20in%20the%20northern%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20where%20the%20humidity%20is%20relatively%20low%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETrees%20and%20shade%20keep%20your%20home%20happy%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrees%20have%20been%20the%20best%20friends%20of%20humans%20since%20the%20beginning%20of%20time.%20From%20giving%20us%20food%20to%20shelter%20under%20its%20shade%2C%20trees%20are%20something%20that%20the%20architects%20advise%20to%20have%20around%20the%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20cannot%20emphasise%20enough%20the%20need%20and%20importance%20of%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F348074%2Fsustainable-home-wayanad-kerala-george-ramapuram-earthitects-hillside-jungle-home-nature%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20trees%20around%20your%20home%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20bring%20in%20shade%2C%20and%20wind%20and%20moderate%20the%20temperature%20around%20them.%20Plant%20as%20many%20trees%20as%20you%20can%20around%20your%20home%20and%20try%20to%20incorporate%20the%20existing%20ones%20in%20the%20design.%20Trust%20me%2C%20they%20are%20going%20to%20be%20a%20lifesaver%20in%20the%20heat%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20George%20Ramapuran%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20sustainable%20design%20firm%2C%20Eartitects.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20built%20numerous%20estates%20around%20the%20theme%20of%20sustainability%20and%20nature%20conservation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgreeing%20with%20George%2C%20Shipra%20also%20emphasises%20the%20importance%20of%20greenery%20to%20keep%20the%20heat%20at%20bay.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20constructing%20the%20home%2C%20you%20can%20always%20look%20at%20the%20region-specific%20trees%20and%20plant%20them%20in%20the%20areas%20where%20your%20home%20will%20have%20verandas%20and%20windows.%20This%20will%20ensure%20shade%20in%20those%20areas%20and%20also%20will%20help%20in%20better%20wind%20circulation%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigur